{"tid":1026721,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"肥人有較大機率係無咩料到","createTime":"2019-02-18T10:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T11:24:30.000Z","uid":123335,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"359ef8e797d27c2a8ba13f1eff9d3db71c162379","tid":1026721,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:14:27.000Z","msg":"Eg. 肥西朗尼,  肥賓, 亞視肥仔，肥貓，欣宜 ...etc <br />\n<br />\n因為肥既原因係食量多&gt;代謝率<br />\n食量過多一般會導致腦部長時間不清醒<br />\n血液長時間走左去胃部幫助消化，而唔係去個腦<br />\n<br />\n以上既人，有部份人士曾經係瘦既時期成功<br />\nEg 肥賓, 朗尼 <br />\n1）圖右：瘦賓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VwrnLcH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVwrnLcH.jpg&h=9c336f6d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n2）圖左：朗尼全盛時期<br />\n圖右：肥西<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9VLWPEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9VLWPEY.jpg&h=fac5fdbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢類人一肥左<br />\n習慣左食量大，習慣左血液長時間流向個胃而非大腦<br />\n會&quot;食老本&quot; 黎扮有料<br />\n不思進取，無再持續進步<br />\n就好似美職朗尼 同意甲呀朗既分別咁"},{"pid":"d8389e6912ef3164e0d5036429dcf692b298ff3f","tid":1026721,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:22:25.000Z","msg":"759呢？"},{"pid":"cdcd27ae07bd0713be3e431079c632896f37e541","tid":1026721,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d8389e6912ef3164e0d5036429dcf692b298ff3f","tid":1026721,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:22:25.000Z","msg":"759呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:26:47.000Z","msg":"唔覺有幾成功"},{"pid":"52effce6c4ffb5c176102dce9e49a6f662b95c91","tid":1026721,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdcd27ae07bd0713be3e431079c632896f37e541","tid":1026721,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d8389e6912ef3164e0d5036429dcf692b298ff3f","tid":1026721,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:22:25.000Z","msg":"759呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":